        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-12-03 23:27:33.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nHmm, I found some strange dentry(namelen != 0, but name is NULL) when I run racer in DNE. Though I did not investigate the real reason why it could happne. \n\nInteresting, I just rerun racer without this patch, it seems the problem is gone. So I will remove this patch from the list.",
